article_title: Virginia warns consumers about health insurance policies pitched by telemarketers
article_text:
Norfolk, VA (23510)

Today

Sun and clouds mixed. High 87F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph..

Tonight

Clear to partly cloudy. Low 62F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph.

article_metadata.author: Elisha Sauers

og.description: Regardless of the sales pitch, the commission says those policies may not be subject to the federal Affordable Care Act, aka Obamacare.
